	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello =)<br><br>Go back to your guild trainer and make sure that you trained one point into it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Because Shamans do get Channeling at level 4 along with all the 5 spell types (Conjuration, Abjuration, Divination, Alteration, and Evocation) If you didnt train in Channeling as you did your 5 spell types, then that could be the reason it's not showing up. =) Hope this helps<br><br>Zeltaria Spiritwalker<br>32th season<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
