	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can do this now at level 43, but I'd certainly recommend that you do it during level 44 and 45 with your new spells:<br><br>Go to Rathe Mountains and fight the trolls in the valley west of the central bug pillar.<br><br>You'll level up pretty fast, but you'll be taking some hits as you go.&nbsp;&nbsp;And that's the point:  you need to take some hits from tough mobs, in order to improve that defense.<br><br>I had actually maxed defense at 200 by level 44 or 45, with this strategy.<br><br>I've written up a fairly detailed guide for soloing the trolls, if people are interested:<br><br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/zones.html?zstrat=26" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/zones.html?zstrat=26</a><br>&nbsp;<br>Macnair (le Grand Mac)<br>Shaman 54<br>Officier de la guilde Union Divine <br>sur Vazaelle</td></tr>
